snippet: Alaska's Democratic and independent candidates for governor have decided to team up as running mates in the upcoming November election in a rare deal aimed at defeating the conservative state's Republican incumbent....

headline.print_headline: Democrat, Independent Join Forces to Unseat Alaska Governor
headline.main: Democrat, Independent Join Forces to Unseat Alaska Governor

lead_paragraph: Alaska's Democratic and independent candidates for governor have decided to team up as running mates in the upcoming November election in a rare deal aimed at defeating the conservative state's Republican incumbent.
